page_content='Sub PreZero(byval proc_num as integer, byval n_char as integer, byref pre_str as string)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Global.pac'}
page_content='\tDim org_len as integer' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Global.pac'}
page_content='\tDim tmp_str as string' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Global.pac'}
page_content='\ttmp_str = CStr(proc_num)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Global.pac'}
page_content='\torg_len = len(tmp_str)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Global.pac'}
page_content='\tpre_str = tmp_str' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Global.pac'}
page_content='\twhile org_len < n_char' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Global.pac'}
page_content='\t\tpre_str = "0" + pre_str' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Global.pac'}
page_content='\t\torg_len = org_len + 1' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Global.pac'}
page_content='\twend' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Global.pac'}
page_content='End Sub' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Global.pac'}

page_content='Sub SwitchRecipe(byval is_from_db as integer, byval recipe_name as string)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}

page_content="\t\t'exe_str " metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}

page_content='NAME ' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}

page_content='WHERE ' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='NAME ' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='like ' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='" ' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='+ "' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\\"" ' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='+ ' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='gActiveProduct ' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='+ "' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\\_%" ' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='+ "' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}

page_content='active=1"\t\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}

page_content='\t\t\'if combo_name = "" then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content="\t\t'\tMessagePopup(83)" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content="\t\t'end if" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}

page_content='\t\tprint "C125,", gActiveProduct, ",", VIO_HMI_RESPONSE' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\'print "C125,A,", VIO_HMI_RESPONSE' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}

page_content='\t\tResetVioAndWait(VIO_HMI_RESPONSE)\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\t\tprint "HMI response gActiveRecipe=", gActiveRecipe' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\t\tif gActiveRecipe = "" then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tMessagePopup(83)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}

page_content='\t\t\tcombo_name = gActiveProduct + "__" + gActiveRecipe' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tprint "combo_name=", combo_name\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\telse' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\t\tgActiveRecipe = recipe_name' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\t\tcombo_name = gActiveProduct + "__" + gActiveRecipe' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\tprint "Active Recipe=", gActiveRecipe\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\tprint "combo_name=", combo_name' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\trtn_str = db_file.' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='get_db("Settings", "NAME", combo_name , "S")' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\tgRecipeS = Cint(rtn_str)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\tif gRecipeS = SIDE_T then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\t\tAssignPlatformEnum(T_000)\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\telseif gRecipeS = SIDE_B then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\t\tAssignPlatformEnum(B_000)\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\telse' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\t\tprint "ERROR"' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='\t\tdb_file.' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}
page_content='close()\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}

page_content="'Sub ArmMoveToPCB(byval arm_id as integer, byval pt_idx as integer)" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tDim target_pos as position" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tTakeArm arm_id" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tif arm_id =0 then\t\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content="'\t\tLetX target_pos =  PosX(ORG_POSITION) - gPcbPointY[pt_idx]" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\telse" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content="'\t\tLetX target_pos =  PosX(ORG_POSITION) + gPcbPointY[pt_idx]" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tend if" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tLetZ target_pos =  PosZ(ORG_POSITION) ' Move to contact position with slow speed" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tGiveArm arm_id" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tArmMoveToPos(arm_id, target_pos, 0, 0)" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'End Sub" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content='Sub MoveArmIndex(byval x_index as double,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content=' byval y_index as double,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tLetX target_pos = PosX(target_pos) + x_index' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content='\t\t\tdelay 100' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tLetZ target_pos = PosZ(target_pos) - z_index' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tGiveArm ARM_0' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='End Sub' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content="'Sub MoveArmToPointDirectly(byval arm_id as integer, byval pt_idx as integer)" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tArmMoveToPos(arm_id, P[pt_idx, arm_id], 1)" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'End Sub" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="' ============" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='Sub ArmMoveToPos(byval cmd_pos as position, byval direct as integer, byval opt as integer)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim current_pos as position' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim target_pos as position' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim current_h as double' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim target_h as double\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim THRESHOLD_H as double' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim spd as integer' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim new_target_h as double' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tspd= 80' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tTHRESHOLD_H = 10' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tTakeArm ARM_0' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t'current_pos = cmd_pos" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tcurrent_pos = CurPos(ARM_0)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tcurrent_h = PosZ(current_pos)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\ttarget_h = PosZ(cmd_pos)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\ttarget_pos = current_pos' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tif direct = 1 then\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tif current_h < target_h then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tLetZ target_pos =  target_h' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\telse' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tif current_h < (target_h + THRESHOLD_H) then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t\t\tnew_target_h = target_h + 20'THRESHOLD_H" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tif new_target_h >= Z_POS_LIMIT then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\tnew_target_h = Z_POS_LIMIT - 1' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tLetZ target_pos =  new_target_h' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t'----------------------------------------------" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tif direct = 1 then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tif opt = MOVE_Y_THEN_X_Z then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t\t\tLetY target_pos =  PosY(cmd_pos) ' Move Y first" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\telse' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t\tLetX target_pos =  PosX(cmd_pos) ' Move X first\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tLetY target_pos =  PosY(cmd_pos)\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content='\tDim gPcbPointX[2], gPcbPointY[2] as double' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tprint "===== TwoPointTeach ====="' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tgPcbPointX[0] = gMarkX[gPlatformSide, 0]' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content='\tgPcbPointX[1] = gMarkX[gPlatformSide, 1]' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content='\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\ttheta1 = atan(Abs(gPcbPointX[1]-gPcbPointX[0])/Abs(gPcbPointY[1]-gPcbPointY[0]))/RAD' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tprint "theta1=", theta1' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tif (gPlatformEnum = T_000) or (gPlatformEnum = B_000) then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\ttheta3 = atan(Abs(gArmPointY[1]-gArmPointY[0])/Abs(gArmPointX[1]-gArmPointX[0]))/RAD\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\telse' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\ttheta3 = atan(Abs(gArmPointX[1]-gArmPointX[0])/Abs(gArmPointY[1]-gArmPointY[0]))/RAD\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tprint "theta3=", theta3' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tif gPcbPointX[1] > gPcbPointX[0] then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="\t\t' Zagato Top FD2 > FD3" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="\t\t' Zagato Bottom FD4 > FD6" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="\t\t' Zenvo Bottom no_refdes+6 > TP32" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="\t\t'theta_d = theta3 - theta1 " metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tTd = theta3 - theta1' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\telse' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="\t        ' Zenvo TP15 < TP19" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="\t\t'theta_d = theta1 - theta3" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tTd = theta1 - theta3' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tgThetaDs = Td' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content='\t\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="\t' new version" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tfor idx = 0 to 1\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tXn = gArmPointX[idx]' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tYn = gArmPointY[idx]' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tLn = hypot(gPcbPointX[idx], gPcbPointY[idx])' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tTn = atan(Abs(gPcbPointX[idx]/gPcbPointY[idx]))/RAD' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tcos_sum = Ln * cos((Tn + Td) * RAD)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tcos_sub = Ln * cos((Tn - Td) * RAD)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tsin_sum = Ln * sin((Tn + Td) * RAD)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tsin_sub = Ln * sin((Tn - Td) * RAD)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tif gPlatformEnum = T_000 then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content='\t\t\t\tXo = Xn + cos_sub' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\tYo = Yn - sin_sub' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content="'\t\t\t\tXo = Xn + sin_sum" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content="'\t\t\telseif (gPcbPointX[idx] < 0) and (gPcbPointY[idx] < 0) then ' Quadrant 3" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\t\tXo = Xn + sin_sub" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\t\tYo = Yn - cos_sub\t\t\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\telse ' Quadrant 4" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\t\tXo = Xn - sin_sum" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\t\tYo = Yn - cos_sum\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\tend if\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tXorg[idx] = Xo' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tYorg[idx] = Yo' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tprint "ORG[", idx, "]=( ", Xo, " , ", Yo, " )"' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tnext idx' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tLetX ORG_POSITION = (Xorg[0] + Xorg[1])/2' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tLetY ORG_POSITION = (Yorg[0] + Yorg[1])/2' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tprint "ORG_POSITION=", ORG_POSITION' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tRefreshHmiOrgPos()' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='End Sub' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='Sub GetPreciseOffset(byval arm_id as integer,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content=' byval x_sym as double,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content=' byval y_sym as double,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content=' byref x_offset as double,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content=' byref y_offset as double)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tDim Xn as double' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tDim Yn as double' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tDim Tr as double' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tTr = gThetaDs * RAD' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tXn = x_sym * cos(Tr) - y_sym * sin(Tr)\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tYn = y_sym * cos(Tr) + x_sym * sin(Tr)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tif gPlatformEnum = T_000 then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tx_offset = (-1) * Yn' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\ty_offset = Xn' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tprint "A00, Precise Offset:(", x_offset, ",", y_offset, ")"' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\telseif gPlatformEnum = A_90 then" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\tx_offset = (-1) * Xn" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\ty_offset = (-1) * Yn\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\'\t\tprint "A90, Precise Offset:(", x_offset, ",", y_offset, ")"' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\telseif gPlatformEnum = B_000 then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tx_offset = (-1) * Yn' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\ty_offset = (-1) * Xn' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tprint "B00, Precise Offset:(", x_offset, ",", y_offset, ")"' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\telseif gPlatformEnum = B_90 then" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\tx_offset = Xn" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\ty_offset = (-1) * Yn\t\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\'\t\tprint "B90, Precise Offset:(", x_offset, ",", y_offset, ")"' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tend if ' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='End Sub' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content='\tSendScaleToVision(arm_id)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Calibration.pac'}

page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Calibration.pac'}

page_content='\tWAIT VIO_VISION_SCALE_ACK, LOW' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Calibration.pac'}
page_content='\tWAIT VIO_VISION_SCALE_ACK, HIGH' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Calibration.pac'}

page_content='0' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}

page_content='\t\ttmp_pos = interval*idx' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}
page_content='\t\tif axis_no = 0 then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}

page_content='\t\t\tLetX target_pos = dest' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}
page_content='\t\telseif axis_no = 1 then\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tdest = cur_posY+tmp_pos' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tLetY target_pos = dest' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}

page_content='\t\t\tdest = cur_posZ-tmp_pos' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tLetZ target_pos = dest' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}

page_content='\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=20' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}
page_content='\t\tdelay 3000' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Tuning.pac'}

page_content='\twhile org_len < n_char' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Global.pac'}
page_content='\t\tpre_str = "0" + pre_str' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Global.pac'}

page_content='\\"" ' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}

page_content='End Function' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Database.pac'}

page_content='Sub RetractArm()' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim target_pos as position' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tTakeArm ARM_0' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\ttarget_pos = CurPos(ARM_0)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tLetZ target_pos =  PosZ(SAFE_POSITION) ' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=100' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tMove P,@E,SAFE_POSITION,S=100\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tGiveArm ARM_0\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='End Sub' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content='\t\ttarget_pos = CurPos(ARM_0)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tLetZ target_pos =  PosZ(SAFE_POSITION)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content="' ============" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'Sub ArmMoveToPCB(byval arm_id as integer, byval pt_idx as integer)" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tDim target_pos as position" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tTakeArm arm_id" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tif arm_id =0 then\t\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\t\tLetY target_pos =  PosY(ORG_POSITION) - gPcbPointX[pt_idx]" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\t\tLetX target_pos =  PosX(ORG_POSITION) - gPcbPointY[pt_idx]" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\telse" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\t\tLetY target_pos =  PosY(ORG_POSITION) + gPcbPointX[pt_idx]" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\t\tLetX target_pos =  PosX(ORG_POSITION) + gPcbPointY[pt_idx]" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tend if" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tLetZ target_pos =  PosZ(ORG_POSITION) ' Move to contact position with slow speed" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tGiveArm arm_id" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="'\tArmMoveToPos(arm_id, target_pos, 0, 0)" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content='Sub MoveArmIndex(byval x_index as double,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content=' byval y_index as double,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content=' byval z_index as double,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content=' byval z_goback as integer,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content=' byval spd as integer)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim target_pos as position' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tTakeArm ARM_0\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tprint "MoveArmIndex,", x_index, ",", y_index, ",", z_index' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content='\t\ttarget_pos = CurPos(ARM_0)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tLetZ target_pos = PosZ(target_pos) + z_index' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tdelay 100' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tLetX target_pos = PosX(target_pos) + x_index' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tLetY target_pos = PosY(target_pos) + y_index\t\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tif z_goback then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tdelay 100' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tLetZ target_pos = PosZ(target_pos) - z_index' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tGiveArm ARM_0' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='End Sub' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content="'Sub MoveArmToPointDirectly(byval arm_id as integer, byval pt_idx as integer)" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content="' ============" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='Sub ArmMoveToPos(byval cmd_pos as position, byval direct as integer, byval opt as integer)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim current_pos as position' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim target_pos as position' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim current_h as double' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim target_h as double\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim THRESHOLD_H as double' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim spd as integer' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim new_target_h as double' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tspd= 80' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tTHRESHOLD_H = 10' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tTakeArm ARM_0' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t'current_pos = cmd_pos" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tcurrent_pos = CurPos(ARM_0)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tcurrent_h = PosZ(current_pos)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\ttarget_h = PosZ(cmd_pos)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\ttarget_pos = current_pos' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tif direct = 1 then\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tif current_h < target_h then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tLetZ target_pos =  target_h' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\telse' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content='\tprint "theta1=", theta1' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tif (gPlatformEnum = T_000) or (gPlatformEnum = B_000) then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content='\telse' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\ttheta3 = atan(Abs(gArmPointX[1]-gArmPointX[0])/Abs(gArmPointY[1]-gArmPointY[0]))/RAD\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tprint "theta3=", theta3' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tif gPcbPointX[1] > gPcbPointX[0] then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="\t\t' Zagato Top FD2 > FD3" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="\t\t' Zagato Bottom FD4 > FD6" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="\t\t' Zenvo Bottom no_refdes+6 > TP32" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content='\telse' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content="\t\t'theta_d = theta1 - theta3" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tTd = theta1 - theta3' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content='\tfor idx = 0 to 1\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tXn = gArmPointX[idx]' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tYn = gArmPointY[idx]' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content='\t\tTn = atan(Abs(gPcbPointX[idx]/gPcbPointY[idx]))/RAD' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tcos_sum = Ln * cos((Tn + Td) * RAD)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tcos_sub = Ln * cos((Tn - Td) * RAD)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tsin_sum = Ln * sin((Tn + Td) * RAD)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tsin_sub = Ln * sin((Tn - Td) * RAD)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tif gPlatformEnum = T_000 then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content='\t\t\t\tXo = Xn + cos_sub' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\tYo = Yn - sin_sub' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="\t\t\telseif (gPcbPointX[idx] < 0) and (gPcbPointY[idx] > 0) then ' Quadrant 2" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\tXo = Xn + cos_sum' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content='\t\t\t\tXo = Xn - cos_sub' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content="'\t\t\t\tXo = Xn - sin_sub" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\t\tYo = Yn - cos_sub\t\t\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\telse ' Quadrant 4" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content="\t\t\telseif (gPcbPointX[idx] < 0) and (gPcbPointY[idx] > 0) then ' Quadrant 2" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\tXo = Xn + cos_sum' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\tYo = Yn - sin_sum' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="\t\t\telseif (gPcbPointX[idx] < 0) and (gPcbPointY[idx] < 0) then ' Quadrant 3" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\tXo = Xn - cos_sub' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\tYo = Yn - sin_sub\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="\t\t\telse ' Quadrant 4" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\tXo = Xn - cos_sum' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\tYo = Yn + sin_sum\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tend if\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\telseif gPlatformEnum = B_90 then" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\tif (gPcbPointX[idx] > 0) and (gPcbPointY[idx] > 0) then ' Quadrant 1" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\t\tXo = Xn - sin_sub" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\t\tYo = Yn + cos_sub" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\telseif (gPcbPointX[idx] < 0) and (gPcbPointY[idx] > 0) then ' Quadrant 2" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\t\tXo = Xn + sin_sum" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\t\tYo = Yn + cos_sum" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\telseif (gPcbPointX[idx] < 0) and (gPcbPointY[idx] < 0) then ' Quadrant 3" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\t\tXo = Xn + sin_sub" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\t\tYo = Yn - cos_sub\t\t\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\telse ' Quadrant 4" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\t\tXo = Xn - sin_sum" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\t\tYo = Yn - cos_sum\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\t\tend if\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tXorg[idx] = Xo' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tYorg[idx] = Yo' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tprint "ORG[", idx, "]=( ", Xo, " , ", Yo, " )"' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tnext idx' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tLetX ORG_POSITION = (Xorg[0] + Xorg[1])/2' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tLetY ORG_POSITION = (Yorg[0] + Yorg[1])/2' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tprint "ORG_POSITION=", ORG_POSITION' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content='Sub GetPreciseOffset(byval arm_id as integer,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content=' byval x_sym as double,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content=' byval y_sym as double,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content=' byref x_offset as double,' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content=' byref y_offset as double)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tDim Xn as double' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tDim Yn as double' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tDim Tr as double' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tTr = gThetaDs * RAD' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tXn = x_sym * cos(Tr) - y_sym * sin(Tr)\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tYn = y_sym * cos(Tr) + x_sym * sin(Tr)' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tif gPlatformEnum = T_000 then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tx_offset = (-1) * Yn' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\ty_offset = Xn' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tprint "A00, Precise Offset:(", x_offset, ",", y_offset, ")"' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\telseif gPlatformEnum = A_90 then" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\tx_offset = (-1) * Xn" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\ty_offset = (-1) * Yn\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\'\t\tprint "A90, Precise Offset:(", x_offset, ",", y_offset, ")"' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\telseif gPlatformEnum = B_000 then' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tx_offset = (-1) * Yn' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\ty_offset = (-1) * Xn' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tprint "B00, Precise Offset:(", x_offset, ",", y_offset, ")"' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\telseif gPlatformEnum = B_90 then" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\tx_offset = Xn" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\ty_offset = (-1) * Yn\t\t" metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\'\t\tprint "B90, Precise Offset:(", x_offset, ",", y_offset, ")"' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tend if ' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='End Sub' metadata={'source': 'emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}

page_content='Sub ArmMoveToPos(byval cmd_pos as position, byval direct as integer, byval opt as integer)' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim current_pos as position' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim target_pos as position' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim current_h as double' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim target_h as double\t\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim THRESHOLD_H as double' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim spd as integer' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tDim new_target_h as double' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tspd= 80' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tTHRESHOLD_H = 10' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tTakeArm ARM_0' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t'current_pos = cmd_pos" metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tcurrent_pos = CurPos(ARM_0)' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tcurrent_h = PosZ(current_pos)' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\ttarget_h = PosZ(cmd_pos)' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\ttarget_pos = current_pos' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tif direct = 1 then\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tif current_h < target_h then' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tLetZ target_pos =  target_h' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\telse' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tif current_h < (target_h + THRESHOLD_H) then' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t\t\tnew_target_h = target_h + 20'THRESHOLD_H" metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tif new_target_h >= Z_POS_LIMIT then' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\tnew_target_h = Z_POS_LIMIT - 1' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tend if' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tLetZ target_pos =  new_target_h' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd\t\t\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tend if' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t'----------------------------------------------" metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tif direct = 1 then' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tif opt = MOVE_Y_THEN_X_Z then' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t\t\tLetY target_pos =  PosY(cmd_pos) ' Move Y first" metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\telse' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t\tLetX target_pos =  PosX(cmd_pos) ' Move X first\t" metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tLetY target_pos =  PosY(cmd_pos)\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd \t\t\t\t\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tend if' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t'----------------------------------------------\t\t\t" metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tif direct = 1 then' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tMove P,@E,cmd_pos,S=spd' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\telse\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tnew_target_h = PosZ(cmd_pos) + 1' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tif new_target_h >= Z_POS_LIMIT then' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\tnew_target_h = Z_POS_LIMIT - 1' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tend if' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tLetZ target_pos =  new_target_h' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t\t'LetZ target_pos =  PosZ(cmd_pos) + 1\t\t" metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=spd' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t\t' Move to pre-calibration contact position\t" metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content="\t\tLetZ target_pos =  PosZ(cmd_pos) ' Move to contact position with slow speed\t\t" metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\tMove P,@E,target_pos,S=2' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tend if' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\tGiveArm ARM_0' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}
page_content='End Sub' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content='\t\tResetVioAndWait(VIO_AUTO_CALI_RESPONSE)\t\t\t\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Arm.pac'}

page_content='Sub GetPreciseOffset(byval arm_id as integer,' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content=' byval x_sym as double,' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content=' byval y_sym as double,' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content=' byref x_offset as double,' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content=' byref y_offset as double)' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tDim Xn as double' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tDim Yn as double' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tDim Tr as double' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tTr = gThetaDs * RAD' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tXn = x_sym * cos(Tr) - y_sym * sin(Tr)\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tYn = y_sym * cos(Tr) + x_sym * sin(Tr)' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\tif gPlatformEnum = T_000 then' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tx_offset = (-1) * Yn' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\ty_offset = Xn' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tprint "A00, Precise Offset:(", x_offset, ",", y_offset, ")"' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\telseif gPlatformEnum = A_90 then" metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\tx_offset = (-1) * Xn" metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content="'\t\ty_offset = (-1) * Yn\t" metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\'\t\tprint "A90, Precise Offset:(", x_offset, ",", y_offset, ")"' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\telseif gPlatformEnum = B_000 then' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
page_content='\t\tx_offset = (-1) * Yn' metadata={'source': './docs/emotion/BGA_CIM/Formula.pac'}
